Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:48.19,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}激情 干渴若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:51.02,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}阖上双目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.46,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}罪孽深重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.37,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:08.34,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你的气味 令人发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:12.34,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}真夜中醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:15.50,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}疯狂 爱 一并饮干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.54,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}投入这臂弯中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.70,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"那边的黑暗是苦涩的"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:27.47,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你惶然不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:31.10,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}即将要迎来永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.35,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"这边的黑暗是甜美的"
