Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然的辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小徹他...死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是图书馆的那个...
